quran[110]{c,v,t}:
  18,1,"Jettooje ngodanii Alla, On jippin…óo e dow Jeyaa…óo makko on deftere nden o wa…óanaani nde oo√Īaare."
  18,2,"Feewnde fii yo o [Nulaa…óo on] hul…ďinir lepte cattu…óe immorde ka makko o weltinira gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen, …ďe no golla Mo∆ī∆īu…ói …óin won'de no woodani …ďe njoddi mo∆ī∆īiri."
  18,3,"Ko …ďe √Īii…ďoo…ďe e ndeer makko [dokke] poomaa."
  18,4,"O reentina …ďen wi""i…ďe: ""Alla jogitike …ďi…ó…óo""."
  18,5,"Ganndal alanaa…ďe e mun, wonaa baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe woodani, mawnii konngol gon'ngol e yaltude e kunndu…óe ma…ď…ďe, …ďe kaalaani si wonaa fenaande."
  18,6,"Mbele jo'o aan a tanpinat hoore-maa e dow batteeji ma…ď…ďe, si ngooŇč…óinaani ndee Yewtere ka suno."
  18,7,"Minen min mba…óii ko woni ko ka hoore leydi cu…óaari mayri, fii yo min mjarribo …ďe ko hommbo e ma…ď…ďe …ďurata mo∆ī∆īin'de golle."
  18,8,"Minen ko min wa…óoo…ďe ko woni kon e hoore mayri boowol joorungal."
  18,9,"Kaa a sikku no yim…ďe fammeere=wimmba nden e binndi …óin, …óuum wonu immorde e aayeeje amen kaawnii…óe?"
  18,10,"Tuma nde sukaa…ďe …ďen cornoo to wimmbo, …ďe mbi'i: ""Joomi amen okku men immorde ka maa…óa Hinnayee=yurmeende newinanaa amen kadi e fiyaake amen peewal."
  18,11,"Min piyi e dow noppi ma…ď…ďe …ói to ndeer wimbo he limoore duu…ďi."
  18,12,"Refti min n immintini …ďe fii yo min pen√Īinir gonndal ko honnde e mojobe=pelle …óen …ói…ói …ďuri moftude [limoore] ko …ďe √Īii…ďi kon dummunne."
  18,13,"Minen Mi…óen pillanaade ma kumpital fii ma…ď…ďe e Goonga, …ďen …óoon, ko sukaa…ďe gooŇč…óin…ďe Joomi ma…ď…ďe min …ďeydani …ďe Peewal."
  18,14,"Min ka…ď…ďi e dow …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe tuma nde …ďe darinoo, …ďe mb'i: ""Joomi amen ko Jey…óo o kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin, men noddataa ko woori Mo dewetee…ói, gooŇč…óii haray men mb'ii ontuma [konngol] pantungol."
  18,15,"∆Āee yim…ďe amen, …ďe jogitike ko woori Mo dewetee…ói, ko haaanunoo ko yo …ďe ngddu e dow ma…ď…ďe dalil …ďanngu…óo. Ko hommbo …ďuri too√Īde ko foti e on pekindii…óo fenaande o fawi e Alla."
  18,16,"Tuma nde mgo…ó…óitino…óon …ďe e ko …ďe ndewata ko ko woori Alla, …ďe coroyi to wimbo Joomi mon fontani on e Yurmeende makko nden o newinani on e fiyaake mon neweende."
  18,17,"Ha…óa yi'a naange nge si nge ∆īellitike henge naayora ka wimbo ma…ď…ďe seŇčgo √Īaamo, si henge mutude nge mutirana …ďe ka seŇčgo nano, kam…ďe he…ďe e yaajeende e …óum, ko jeyaa…óum e kaawisaji Alla, on mo Alla feewni ko on woni peew…óo, kala mo,o majjini a he…ďantaa mo kee…óo perwnoowo."
  18,18,"Ha…óa sikka …ďe ko …ďe fin…ďe, tawi kam…ďe ko …ďe …óaanii…ďe, Mi…óen mbylitira …ďe seŇčgo √Īaamo e seŇčgo nano, rawaandu ma…ď…ďe ndu no fori koy…óe ndun …óe ka dammbugal, si a ∆īellitike e ma…ď…ďe a ruŇčtotono e ma…ď…ďe ndogaa a heewatno kulol immorde e ma…ď…ďe."
  18,19,"Ko nii Min immintiniri …ďe fii yo …ďe la…ďnondir hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, bi'oowo wi'i e ma…ď…ďe: ""No foti heewde ko √Īii…ď…óon?"" ∆Āe mbi'i: ""Min √Īii…ďii √Īallal maa go…ó…óum e √Īallal."" ∆Āe mbi'i: ""Ko Joomi mon woni nganndu…óo emmbere ko √Īii…ďu…óon, nulee go…ó…óo e mon won'dude e …óii kaaki=ceede mon …óoo ka saare, yo o ndaaru ko hommbo e ma…ď…ďe …ďuri laa…ďde √Īaamitee, yo o addan on √Īaametee immorde e on …óon, yo o molto wata go'oto tin fii mon."
  18,20,"Pellet, kam…ďe si …ďe ∆īellitike e mon …ďe pi…óat on, ma …ďe ndutta on e laawol ma…ď…ďe ngol, on tuma on maletaake poomaa."
  18,21,"Ko nii min n njaltiniri fii ma…ď…ďe, fii yo …ďe nganndu pellet, Fodoore Alla nde ko nde Goonga, Pellet, Darnga sikke alaa e maggal. Tuma nde …ďe poo…óondiratnoo hakkunde ma…ď…ďe fiyaake ma…ď…ďe …óen, …ďe mbi'i'i: ""Mahee e hoore ma…ď…ďe maadi, ko Joomi ma…ď…ďe woni ganndu…óo fii ma…ď…ďe."" ∆Āe fool…ďe e fiyaake mu'un mbi'i i: ""Min njogitoto e dow ma…ď…ďe Juulirde."""
  18,22,"Aray …ďe mbi'a: ""Ko …ďe tato naya…ďo ma…ď…ďe ko rawaandu ma…ď…ďe ndu."" ∆Āe mbi'a kadi: ""Ko …ďe njowo njeega…ďo ma…ď…ďe ko rawaandu ma…ď…ďe ndu ko fampaangol e ni…ďe."" ∆Āe mbi'a kadi: ""Ko …ďe njee…ói…óo njeetata…ďo ma…ď…ďe ko rawaandu ma…ď…ďe ndun."" Maaku: ""Ko Joomi an woni ganndu…óo limoore ma…ď…ďe, anndaa …ďe si wonaa see…óaa…ďe."" Wata a wee√Īju fii ma…ď…ďe si wonaa yewtere fee√Īnde, wota a lanndo fii ma…ď…ďe hay e gooto e ma…ď…ďe."
  18,23,"Wota a wi'an huunde: ""Min mi mba…óay …óum janngo."""
  18,24,"Si wonaa si Alla Muuyii, janto Joomi maa…óa si a yejjitii, maaku: ""No tijjaa nde Joomi an Feewnan mi ko …ďuri …ďadaade immorde e …óum Peewal."""
  18,25,"∆Āe √Īii…ďi ka wimbo ma…ď…ďe duu…ďi teeme…ó…óe tati, …ďe …ďeydi jeenay."
  18,26,"Maaku: ""Ko Alla woni ganndu…óo emmbere ko …ďe √Īii…ďi, ko KaŇčko heeranii ko wirnii ko ka kammuuji e ka leydi kaawes ko yi'iri wa makko e ko naniri, alanaa …ďe ga makko gi…óo, o kafidaa e √Īaawoore makko he hay gooto."
  18,27,"Janngu ko wahayinaa e maa…óa ko immorde e deftere Joomi maa nden, alaa wattitoowo Daaluyeeji=konngudi Makko …óin, a he…ďataa ga makko fattorde."
  18,28,"Tabintin woŇčkii maa…óa kin won'dude e …ďen noddoo…ďe Joomi ma…ď…ďe ka bimmbi e ka kiikii…óe he…ďe faandii Jaati makko Kin, wota gite maa …óe njawtu ga ma…ď…ďe hara ha…óa fa'andii cu…óaari nguurndam aduna, wota a …óofto on mo Min mbelsindini …ďer…óe mun ga jaŇčtagol Min o njokki belee…óe makko fiyaake makko on woni halkaare."
  18,29,"Maaku Goonga ka immorde ka Joomi mon, mono faalaa yo o gooŇč…óin mono faalaa yo o yeddu, minen min n keblanii too√Īoo…ďe …ďe Yiite no hunnditi …ďe …óen…óe magge …óen si …ďe …óa…ď…ďii faabo, …ďe faaboree Ndiyam mba'u…óam no sila taynaa…óo …óam ju…óa je'ece …óe, bonii njaram bonii werde."
  18,30,"Pellet, …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īi …óin, Minen Min njeebataa njo…ďdi kala mo∆ī∆īin…óo golle."
  18,31,"∆Āeen …óoon no woodani …ďe Aljannaaji √Īii…ďal caatli no ila ley ma…ď…ďe, hi…ďe cu…óiree ton immorde e jaw…óe kanŇče …ďe …ďornoo comci haak…óu…ói …óewlu…ói e jalbu…ói ko …ďe so…ď…ďindii…ďe=tuugiibe ton e hoore julle, mo∆ī∆īii mbarjaari mo∆ī∆īii kadi fooftorde."
  18,32,"fiyan …ďe yeru,wor…ďe …ói…óo min mba…óani go…ó…óo e ma…ď…ďe gese …ói…ói inab Menhunndintini ‚Äúkurliri…óe …óe tamarooje Min mba…ói hakkunde majje remuru."
  18,33,"∆äeen gese …ói…ói kala mgaddi √Īaametee majje, …óe too√Īaani hay e huunde e …óuum, Min ce'eki hakkunde majje [gese …óen …ói…ói] caangol."
  18,34,"Wonani mo dim…óe, o wi'ani gon'diijo makko on tawi himo yewtude mo: ""Miin mi…óo …ďurmaa jawdi e teddude gorol""."
  18,35,"O naati ka ngesa makko tawi ko o too√Ī…óo hoore-makko, o wi'i: ""Mi sikkaani ba re'ay poomaa""."
  18,36,"Mi sikkaani kadai Darnga ngal daroto, mi woo…óndii si mi artira le ka Joomi am, maa mi taw sanne, waylitorde …ďurnde ba mo∆ī∆īude."
  18,37,"Gon'diijo o makko on wi'i mo, tawi homo yewtude mo: ""Enee, a yeddii On Tak…óo ma immorde mbullaari=leydi refti e to…ď…ďere [maniiyu] refti O fotndumaa gorko""."
  18,38,"Kono min ko KaŇčko Alla woni Joomi am, mi kafidataa e Joomi am hay gooto."
  18,39,"Ko haanunoo tuma nde naatu…óaa ka ngesa maa…óa mbi'aa: ""Ko Alla muuyi ko doole alaa si wanaa Alla"". Si a yi'ii kam min mi…óo …ďurmaa fam…óude jawdi e …ďi…ó…ďe."
  18,40,"No jortaa nde Joomi am okkoyta kam mo∆ī∆īere …ďurnde ngesa maa ba O nula e mabba lepte immorde ka kammu ba wonta boowal …ďowrungal."
  18,41,"Maa de ndiyam mabba …óa wonta …ďee…ďu…óam, hara a hattantaa …óa…ď…ďugol …óam."
  18,42,"Dim…óe makko …óen bonnaa o weeti homo waylita newe makko …óen e dow ko o nafki kon e mabba, tawi kammba ko fukkiiba e da∆ī∆īe mabba, homo wi'a: ""Ee haaniina,hara mi kafidaano e Joomi an hay e gooto""."
  18,43,"Laatanaaki mo fedde nde no walla mo ga Alla, o wonaani pool…óo."
  18,44,"No toon Giggol Alla Goongawol ngol ko KaŇčko mo∆ī∆īi mbarjaari mo∆ī∆īi battane."
  18,45,"Fiyan …ďe yeru nguurndam aduna …óam no wa'i wa ndiyam Min njippini…óam immorde ka kammu jillondiri e majjam pu…ói leydi ndin, …ói wonti muncii…ói keneeli no jaroo…ói, Alla wonii ko o kattan…óo e dow kala hu'unde."
  18,46,"Jawdi ndi e …ďi…ó…ďe wor…ďe …ďe ko cu…óaari nguurndam aduna, mo∆ī∆īi keddotoo…ói …óin ko …ói …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude mbarjaari ka Joomi maa…óa e mo∆ī∆īude yela."
  18,47,"√Ďannde min n na…ďata pelle …óen a nji'a leydi ndin ko fee√Īndi, min moo…ďa …ďe Min ngaccataa immorde e ma…ď…ďe hay e gooto."
  18,48,"∆Āe kolliree ka Joomi maa [ko …ďe] saffewol, [O Daalana …ďe] gooŇč…óii on arii e amen wano min n tagirnoo on non, ka laawol adanol, ko woni on aa∆īino won'de min n wa…óanaani on fodoore."
  18,49,"Deftere nde wallinee, a nj'a bon…ďe …ďe ko hul…ďe ko woni kon e mayre, …ďe mbi'a: ""Ee bone amen, ko he…ďi ndee deftere nde …óalataa tosokum wonaa njanum si wonaa nde moftii …óum, …ďe tawa ko …ďe ngolli ko no wee…ďitaa, Joomi maa…óa too√Īataa hay e gooto."
  18,50,"Tuma nde Min mb'annoo maleykaaji: ""cujjanee Aadama, …ďe cujji si wonaa Ibliisa o laatike jeyaa…óo e jinnaaji …óin o yalti e Yamiroore Joomi makko. E on jogitoto mo e …ďi…ó…ďe makko …ďen yi…ó…ďe ga Am, hara kam…ďe ko …ďe a√Ī…ďe mo'on, bonanii too√Īoo…ďe …ďe battudi."
  18,51,"Mi tawnaani …ďe tagugol kammuuji …óin e leydi ndi wonaa tagugol ko'e ma…ď…ďe kadi, Mi wonaani jogitotoo…óo majjinoo…ďe …ďe sembinoo…ďe."
  18,52,"E √Īannde O Daalata: ""Noddee kafidaa…ďe Am …ďe, …ďen …ďe ngaa∆īi…óon, …ďe nodda …ďe, …ďe njaabotaako …ďe min n mba…ói hakkunde ma…ď…ďe halkorde""."
  18,53,"Bon…ďe …ďen nji'a Yiite ngen …ďe pellita won'de kam…ďe ko …ďe ukketee…ďe e magge, …ďe ke…ďataa gaay magge yiiltorde."
  18,54,"GooŇč…óii Min fensitanii yim…ďe …ďen e ndeer ndee Alqur'aanaare immorde e kala yeru, ne…ó…óaŇčke on wonii homo …ďuri kala huunde wennjugol."
  18,55,"Ha…óaani yim…ďe …ďen nde …ďe gooŇč…óinta …ďe insinanoo Joomi ma…ď…ďe tuma nde Peewal ngal arnoo e ma…ď…ďe, si wonaa nde arata e ma…ď…ďe sunna aran…ďe …ďen maa…óun nde arata e ma…ď…ďe lepte …óen ko …óe pee√Īu…óe."
  18,56,"Min Nuliraani Nulaa…ďe …ďe si wonaa ko weltinoo…ďe e jeertinoo…ďe, …ďe heefer…ďe he…ďe wennjana meere nden fii yo …ďe fuynir nde Goonga kan, …ďe njogitii aayeeje Am …óen e ko …ďe mjeertiniraa kon jalnori."
  18,57,"Alaa potat…óo too√Īde on waajuraa…óo aayeeje Joomi makko o …óuurii=fali e gaayi majje o yejjiti ko juu…óe makko …óen ardini kon. Minen Min mba…óii e …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen cokoo…óe fii wota …ďe faamu nde, ka noppi ma…ď…ďe kadi pahu, hay si a noddii …ďe fa'ade e Peewal …ďe peewataa on tuma haapoomaa."
  18,58,"Ko Joomi mon woni cuhroowo ko O Jom yurmeende e on, sinndo O nangitirno …ďe ko …ďe paggitii kon O yaccinanatno …ďe lepte …óe, ko woni, no woodani …ďe fodoore …ďe he…ďataa ga mayre fattorde."
  18,59,"∆äeen ca'e, Min kalkuno …ďe tuma nde …ďe too√Īnoo min mba…óani halkeede ma…ď…ďe nden Fodoore."
  18,60,"Tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo sagata makko on: ""Mi seerataa haa mi yottoo ka fottirde maaje …óe …ói…ói, ma de mi wuloo jamaanu."
  18,61,"Tuma nde …ďe njottoyinoo hakkonde majje …ďe njejjiti li'ingu ma…ď…ďe, ngu jogitii laawol maggol ka maayo wuddere."
  18,62,"Nde …ďe lummbunoo o [Muusaa] maakani sagataa makko on: ""Addan en sojjaari=bottaari men ndi, gooŇč…óii en kawrii e nduu yahdu men …óoo tampere."
  18,63,"O wi'i: ""A yi'ii, nde corno…óen ka fetere, min mi yejjiti …óoon li'ingu o yejjintinaani kam fii maggil si wonaa Seytaane nde mi anndita ngu jogitii laawol maggol nder maayo no haawnori""."
  18,64,"[Muusaa] maaki: ""Ko …óoon ko ngon…óen …óa…ď…ďude kon [woni], …ďe nduuttii e …ďatteeji ma…ď…ďe fillitagol."
  18,65,"∆Āe tawoyi jeyaa…óo immorde e jeyaa…ďe Amen min n ngokki mo jurmeende immorde ka amen, min nganndini mo immorde e amen Ganndal."
  18,66,"Muusaa maakani mo: ""Enee [a accay] mi jokkete fii yo a anndinam go…ó…óum e ko ngandina…óaa kon peewal ewal""?"
  18,67,"[Khadiru] maaki: ""Pellet, aan a hattantaa mu√Īal won'dugol e an""."
  18,68,"Ko honno mu√Īuirtaa e dow kon ko a hu…ďindoraa …óum ganndal?"
  18,69,"[Muusaa] maaki: ""A tawat kam n si Alla Muuyi ko mi mun√Īii…óo, mi yeddataa yamiroore maa""."
  18,70,"O maaki: ""Si a jokkat kam wota a lanndo kan gaayi hu'unde haa mi yeewte immorde e mayre jaŇčta""."
  18,71,"∆Āe njahi haa de …ďe mba…ó…ónoo ka laana o yulika, [Muusaa] maaki: ""A yulii ka fii yo ka yoolu yim…ďe makka?! gooŇč…óii a addii hu'unde mawnde""."
  18,72,"[Khadiru] maaki: ""Enee, mi wi'aano ma pellet, an a hattantaa mu√Īal won'dugol e am""."
  18,73,"[Muusaa] maaki: wota a jogoram ko mi yejjiti kon, wota a hewtinan e fiyaake am on satteende""."
  18,74,"∆Āe njehi haa nde …ďe pottunoo e suka o wari mo! P maakani [mo]: ""E a war woŇčkii laa…ďuki tanaa [yo…ďtanagol] woŇčkii, gooŇč…óii a addii hu'unde a√Īiinde""."
  18,75,"[Khadiru] wi'i: ""Enee, mi wi'aano ma pellet, an a hattantaa mu√Īal won'dugol e am""."
  18,76,"[Muusaa] maaki: ""Si mi lanndike ma gaayi hu'unde …ďaawo …óii, wata a won'dino e am, gooŇč…óii a timminii ngantu e am."
  18,77,"∆Āe njehi haa …ďe njaltiti e yim…ďe saare, …ďe …óa…ď…ďiri …ďe √Īaametee …ďe calii wernude …ďe, …ďe tawi e ndeer mayre maadi faalaa fukkaade [Khadiru] o darnindi , o [Muusaa] maaki: ""Sinno a yi…óno a ∆īettatno njo…ďdi e …óum""."
  18,78,"[Khadiru] maaki: ""Ko …óum woni ceerdigal hakku- nde am e ma'a, mi yeewtu maa firo k ko a hattanaana mun√Īaade e dow mum""."
  18,79,"Si ko laana ka, ka laatanike miskinee…ďe ngollo- …ďe ka maayo, mi faalaa aybin'de ka, hari laatike …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe laam…óo homo nannga kala laana o ja…ďta."
  18,80,"Si ko suka on maw…ďe makko …ďe ngoni gooŇč…óin…ďe , min kuli wata o fawu …ďe bewre e keeferaaku."
  18,81,"Men paalaa nde Joomi ma…ď…ďe wa…ótitanta …ďe …ďur…óo mo mo∆ī∆īude laa…ď…óo e …ďur…óo …ďattaade yurmeende."
  18,82,"Si ko maadi ndin, ndi laatanino sukaa…ďe …ói…óo won'…óu…ďe ka saare, laatii ley mayri ngalu ma…ď…ďe kam…ďe …ói…óo, hari baaba ma…ď…ďe laatinoke mo∆ī∆īo, Joomi maa…óa Faalaa nde …ďe njottotoo sagatalaagu ma…ď…ďe, O yaltina ngalu ma…ď…ďe ngu […óuum] ko Yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa, mi wa…óiraani …óum e yamirooree am, …óuum ko firo kon ko a hattanaani mun√Īaade e dow mum."
  18,83,"He…ďe fa'umaa la…ďndaade fii Julqarnayni, maaku: ""Aray mi jannga e taweede mon e …óum jaŇčta."
  18,84,"Minen, Min wee…ďinanno mo ka leydi, Min ngokki mo immorde e kala hu'unde sabu."
  18,85,"O jokki sabu[laawol}"
  18,86,"Haa nde o yottinoo ka mutirde na'ange ngen o tawi henge muta e loope …ďaleeje, o tawi ton yim…ďe : Min mbi'i'i: ""Ko aan yo jom galaa…ói …ói…ói, ko si a leptay ma si a jogitoto e ma…ď…ďe ko mo∆ī∆īi."
  18,87,"O wi'i: Si tawii ko on too√Īu…óo min lepta mo, refti o ruttee ka Joomi makko o lepta mo lepte a√Īii…óe""."
  18,88,"Si tawii ko on gooŇč…óin…óo o golli ko mo∆ī∆īi no woodani mo njo…ďdi mo∆ī∆īiri ndin, aray min n mbi'ana mo e fiyaake amen on neweende."
  18,89,"Refti o jokki laawol."
  18,90,"Haa de o yottinoo ka ∆īellitorde na'ange nge, o tawi henge ∆īellitoo e dow yim…ďe, Min mba…óanaani …ďe ga magge hee…óo."
  18,91,"Ko wano nii, goo…óii Min ku…ďindike ko woni kon ka makko e ganndal."
  18,92,"Refti o jokki laawol."
  18,93,"Haa nde o yottinoo hakkunde heedooji …ói …ói…óio tawi ga majji yim…ďe …ďe …óe…ďataa faamde konngol."
  18,94,"∆Āe mbi'i: eey ma Julqarnayni, pellet, Yaajuuja e Maajuuja ko bonnoo…ďe ka leydi. Enee, min wa…óante njeenaari fii yo a wa…ó hakkunde amen e ma…ď…ďe heedo?"
  18,95,"O wi'i: ""Ko Joomi am wee…ďinani kan kon …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude, walliree kan doole mi wa…óa hakkunde mo'on e ma…ď…ďe heedo""."
  18,96,"Ngaddanee kam kunte njam…óe haa nde o feppi- ndirnoo hakkunde na…óe …óen …ói…ói, o wi'i: ""pifee haa nde o wa…ónoo …óum yiite, o wi'i: ngaddanee kam sila mi wancina e dow mum""."
  18,97,"∆Āe kattantaa ∆īellitagol ndi, …ďe hattantaa kadi julgol ndi."
  18,98,"O wi'i: …óum …óoo ko Yurmeende immornde e Joomi am, si Fodoore Joomi am nden arii o wa…óat [heedo] ngo …óiggungo, Fodoore Joomi am nde laatike ko nde Goonga""."
  18,99,"Min …óala yoga e ma…ď…ďe nden √Īalnde no yolloo e yoga, wuttaa ka allaadu Min moo…ďa …ďe moo…ďudee."
  18,100,"Min wee…ďitanat(holliray) Jahannama nden √Īannde yeddu…ďe …ďen wee…ďitugol=holllirgol."
  18,101,"∆Āeen …ďe gite mue'n laatii e wirngallo gaayi jaŇčta Aan, …ďe laati…ďe kattantaa nangol."
  18,102,"Enee, …ďen yeddu…ďe cikku …ďe njogoto jeyaa…ďe Am …ďen ga Am, Minen Min heblanii Jahannama on fii yeddu…ďe…ďen wona werde."
  18,103,"Maaku: ""Taw si min kumpitay on fii …ďur…ďe hayrude(pertude) golle?"""
  18,104,"Ko …ďeen …ďe golle mu'en yeebii ka ngurdam aduna hara kam…ďe he…ďe cikka he…ďe mo∆ī∆īin'de golle."
  18,105,"Ko …ďeen ngoni yeddu…ďe aayeeje Joomi ma…ď…ďe …óen e kawroygol e makko, golle ma…ď…ďe …óen bone Min √Īii…ďinantaa…ďe √Ďande Darngal ∆Āetu."
  18,106,"Jahannama ko …óum woni njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe, sabu ko …ďe njeddi kon …ďe jogitii aayeeje am …óen e Nulaa…ďe am …ďen njalkitde."
  18,107,"Pellet, …ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īi …óin laatanto …ďe Aljannaaji Firdawsi Werdi(jipporde)."
  18,108,"Ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe ndeer ton, …ďe …óa…ď…ďataa gani makko waylitorde."
  18,109,"Maaku: ""Sinno maayo ngo laatino ndaha fii Daaluyeeji Joomi am …ói, maayo ngo re'ayno ko adii ndee re'ata Daaluyeeji Joomi am …óin, sinno Min addii yeru maggo e …ďeydude""."
  18,110,"Maaku: ""Pellet min, ko mi …ďanndiŇčke yeru mon, no wahayineede e am. Pellet, dewetee…óo mon o ko dewetee…óo Gooto, kala jortii…óo kawroyde e Joomi makko yo o gollu golle mo∆ī∆īe wota o kafidu e dewal Joomi makko hay e gooto""."
